<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.10">
<l>parantataṇ paravaiyuḷnīrtoṟum parantuḷaṉ</l>
<l>parantavaṇ ṭamiteṉa nilavicum poḻivaṟak</l>
<l>karantaci liṭantoṟum iṭantikaḻ poruṭoṟuṅ</l>
<l>karanteṅkum parantuḷa ṉivaiyuṇṭa karaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He exists, spread out in every water on the cool expanse that is spread out,</l>
<l>without end earth [and] sky as “this is the cosmic egg that is spread out”,</l>
<l>in any few place that are hidden, in every matter/meaning shining in [those] places,</l>
<l>he exists spread out everywhere in hiding, the Firm one who is [all] these.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
